N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 351.11 - Reporting requirements

State Regulations

Each probation director shall report to the Commissioner of
the Division of Criminal Justice Services in the form, manner, and timeframes
prescribed, including any and all such information requested pertaining to any
person receiving a probation sentence, placed on probation, or subject to
interim probation supervision. Notes
